<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I read Best Served Cold first and it totally works as a stand-alone. I mean, there were bits that made me want to read the trilogy for more depth but <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I read Best Served Cold first and it totally works as a stand-alone. I mean, there were bits that made me want to read the trilogy for more depth but nowhere was I left confused for lack of reading the previous books.<br />I'm now making my way through the trilogy and having read this one first is lending me an interesting perspective. It didn't ruin anything for sure.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
