</a><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/20887238.Traitor_s_Blade__Greatcoats___1_" title="Traitor's Blade (Greatcoats, #1) by Sebastien de Castell" rel="nofollow noopener">
  <img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1441772922l/20887238._SY75_.jpg" alt="Traitor's Blade (Greatcoats, #1) by Sebastien de Castell" class="gr-hostedUserImg">
</a></span>
  <a data-text-id="16845134147450314385" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

